---
title: Pork Schnitzel Patties with Warm Brussels Salad
description: Crispy pork is pretty much perfect in any form, but this isn’t your run-of-the-mill schnitzel.  We're using ground pork to get this German classic on the table as fast as possible!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/galettes-de-porc-style-schnitzel-f25d1e9d.jpg
